::: Pheniox shot her head around ::: What was that?

::: Black Aracnia took out her gun. ::: Ill look into it.

::: She headed down the corridor, and using her scanners, decided the scream 
came from the CR chamber room. She entered to see Quickstrike resting 
comfortably in the chamber. :::

::: Black Aracnia ::: Ah, look at you. Your so...disgusting!

::: Sugar bot walked up to the chamber window and ran her claw down it. She 
was sorry it had to be this way...:::

::: She shot the chamber, causing it to errut into an electrical spitfire. :::
